ced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) and 3 others. Changed since last run: Iaşi (IAS/LRIA), Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Turku (TKU/EFTU), Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Cristiano Ronaldo (FNC/LPMA), Federico Fellini (RMI/LIPR), Bacău George Enescu (BCM/LRBC), Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP), Billund (BLL/EKBI) and 2 others.",
